 1) Primitive data types: The primitive data types include boolean, char, byte, short, integer, long, float and double.
 2) Non-primitive data types: The non-primitive data types include Classes Interfaces and Arrays
 
 
Data Type	Default Value	Default size
boolean	false	1 bit
char	'\u0000'	2 byte
byte	0	1 byte
short	0	2 byte
integer	0	4 byte
long	0L	8 byte
float	0.0f	4 byte
double	0.0d	8 byte